difficulty:
If I didn't have to scroll too much and I could read the info at once it was easier. It also made it easy if there was less text to read. 

Having to search or go back and foreth made it harder because of the small screen.
format: If it was simple and organized and easy to read I was satisfied. A wall of text or having to scroll & remember where I'd been on the page before made me more unsatisfied.
